"1 cup fresh or frozen cranberries","1  bottle (48 oz., 6 cups) cranberry juice cocktail","1/2 cup raisins","4  to 6 cinnamon sticks (about 3 in.)","2  bottles (750 ml.) fruity dry red wine such as Gamay Beaujolais, or 6 cups apple juice and 2 to 4 tablespoons lemon juice, to taste","1/4  to 1/2 cup sugar","1 teaspoon almond extract","  About 3/4 cup orange-flavor liqueur such as Cointreau or triple sec (optional)"